{"parentUuid":"5670869e-6258-47e5-a2ef-a7df9421140a","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a98d53b8f2a71429f","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QuA2eRLgoSRv6eriyZ23GV","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Shopify platform ecosystem model enabling others to build stores 2025 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Digital Ecosystem: 2026 Guide to Business Networks - Shopify\",\"url\":\"https://www.shopify.com/blog/digital-ecosystem\"},{\"title\":\"Shopify Marketing Strategy 2025: Ecosystem, Metrics & Growth\",\"url\":\"https://www.blankboard.studio/originals/blog/shopify-strategy-2025\"},{\"title\":\"Shopify for eCommerce in 2025: Still the #1 Platform to Scale\",\"url\":\"https://www.wgentech.com/growth-hacks/shopify-for-ecommerce-growth/\"},{\"title\":\"Shopify Trends to Watch in 2026 | For Merchants & Developers\",\"url\":\"https://softrop.com/latest-shopify-development-trends-in-2026-for-merchants-and-developers/\"},{\"title\":\"How Shopify’s App Store Shapes the Future of Custom eCommerce\",\"url\":\"https://acowebs.com/shopify-shapes-future-custom-ecommerce/\"},{\"title\":\"Why Shopify Will Dominate eCommerce Growth in 2026?\",\"url\":\"https://www.ayatas.com/why-shopify-will-dominate-ecommerce-growth-in-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"The State of Shopify in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://storeleads.app/reports/shopify\"},{\"title\":\"Emerging 2025 Trends for Thriving Shopify Businesses - TGL\",\"url\":\"https://www.thegenielab.com/blogs/articles/emerging-2025-trends-for-thriving-shopify-businesses\"},{\"title\":\"Verified Shopify Statistics 2026: Facts & Analysis\",\"url\":\"https://thehubcontent.com/news/shopify-statistics-facts-trends-analysis-2025/\"},{\"title\":\"Latest Shopify Statistics, Facts, and Trends in 2025/2026\",\"url\":\"https://craftberry.co/articles/shopify-statistics-facts-and-trends-in-2024-you-don-t-want-to-miss\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about Shopify's platform ecosystem model that enables others to build stores in 2025-2026:\n\n## Shopify's Ecosystem Model\n\nShopify isn't just helping people build online stores anymore, it's quietly becoming the backbone of global commerce. This creates a flywheel effect where easy-to-use tools attract merchants. A growing merchant base makes the platform more valuable for app developers and service partners, who then expand Shopify's App Store and Partner Program with specialized tools.\n\n## Key Ecosystem Components\n\n**App Marketplace:** The Shopify App Store hosts over 12,320 applications as of 2025, representing 27% growth from the previous year. Approximately 87% of merchants utilize at least one application beyond core platform functionality.\n\n**Developer Support:** App developer revenues exceeded $1.5 billion collectively since inception, with Shopify's developer commission structure offering 0% fees for developers earning under $1 million annually.\n\n**Partner Network:** Merchant Solutions includes payments, transaction fees, financing, advertising, and revenue from its expansive partner ecosystem.\n\n## 2025-2026 Evolution\n\nThe Shopify ecosystem is entering a new phase of maturity, defined less by new Shopify features and more by its underlying architecture and data strategy. The conversation has shifted from \"how do we launch faster?\" to \"how do we design an eCommerce system that can adapt continuously?\"\n\nThe 2025 Shopify ecosystem is more than just apps, it's an entire growth stack designed for flexibility and future-proofing. With over 8,000 curated apps and deep integration capabilities, Shopify empowers brands to evolve without overhauling their architecture.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"79502756-f191-4a95-8dcc-19a80895ed1a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:18:37.854Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"5670869e-6258-47e5-a2ef-a7df9421140a","userType":